```plantuml
@startuml open-risk_Open_Risk_API

component "Client Applications" {
    component "API Explorer (Python Client)" as client_explorer
    component "LibreOffice Macros" as libreoffice_macros
}

component "Model Server" {
    component "Flask Application" as flask_app
    component "RDFlib" as rdflib
    component "Concentration Metrics Library" as concentration_lib
    database "Model Definitions (RDF)" as model_defs
}

component "Data Server" {
    component "Python-Eve Application" as eve_app
    database "MongoDB" as mongodb
}

component "OpenCPM Suite" {
    component "NPL Concentration" as npl_concentration {
        component "Model Server" as opencpm_model_server
        component "Compute Engine" as compute_engine
        component "Model Definitions" as opencpm_models
    }
}

client_explorer --> flask_app : REST API (HTTP)
client_explorer --> eve_app : REST API (HTTP)
libreoffice_macros --> flask_app : REST API (HTTP)
libreoffice_macros --> eve_app : REST API (HTTP)

flask_app --> rdflib : Processes
flask_app --> concentration_lib : Calls
flask_app --> model_defs : Reads/Writes

eve_app --> mongodb : Persists data

opencpm_model_server --> compute_engine : Calls
opencpm_model_server --> opencpm_models : Reads
opencpm_model_server --> flask_app : Extends

@enduml
```